title: Inject channel attachment syntax into prompt
---
When a message includes attachments, inject a block into the system prompt (or pre-user-turn context) documenting the available attachment reference syntax: [FILE:/path], [IMAGE:/path], [VOICE:/path], [DOCUMENT:/path], [AUDIO:/path]. The agent must know these tokens exist before it sees them in a message.